==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Express train
<hw>Express train</hw>. <def>Formerly, a railroad train run expressly
for the occasion; a special train; now, a train run at express or
special speed and making few stops.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expressure</ent>⟦br⟧
